🛡‍‍ *Bulletproof*:  
  
▪️ Bulletproof has a shield that saves him agaist death just one time.
  
▪ Bulletproof loses the shield if mafia shots them. 
  
▪️ if the people want to execute the bulletproof at day, the bulletproof will not die and the bot announce that chosen player is the bulletproof.
  
▪️ when bulletproof loses the shield, the mafia team can kill them.  